description:
WARNING: Both Blender 4.5 and this version of Cats Blender Plugin are in early Alpha stage. Expect bugs, crashes, and other issues during usage.

Known Incompatible Addons: Official Cats Blender Plugin and MMD Tools may cause conflicts as this version includes its own MMD Tools implementation.

For support, please use the Unofficial Cats Discord for known issues.

Do not ask for help with the unofficial version in the official Cats Discord server.
